Generate sinusoidal signal <pre><code>duration = 1;
A = 1;
phi = 0;
fs_continuous = 192000;
f = 10;

[t_continuous, y_continuous] = generate_sine(duration, A, phi, fs_continuous, f);
</code></pre>

Quantize a signal a using Mid-Rise method <pre><code>[y_midrise, ~] = quantize_signal(x_quant, bits, "mid_rise");
</code></pre> Quantize a signal a using Mid-Tread method <pre><code>[y_midtread, ~] = quantize_signal(x_quant, bits, "mid_tread");
</code></pre>
